Class LocationChangedEvent

java.lang.Object
  edu.nyu.cs.omnidroid.core.Event
      edu.nyu.cs.omnidroid.core.LocationChangedEvent

public class LocationChangedEvent
extends Event

This class encapsulates an LocationChanged event. It wraps the intent that triggered this event and provides access to any attribute data associated with it.
